Alexander Moiseenko vs Kassa Korley
Xtracon Open (2019), Helsingor DEN, rd 4, Jul-22 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Exchange. Positional Variation (D35)


1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. cd5 ed5 5. Bg5 c6 6. e3 Bd6 7. Bd3 O-O 8. Qc2 h6 9. Bh4 Re8 10. Nge2 a5 11. h3 Na6 12. a3 Nc7 13. O-O Ne6 14. f3 Ng5 15. e4 Nfe4 16. fe4 Nh3 17. gh3 Qh4 18. Rf2 Bh3 19. Rd1 Re5 20. de5 Bc5 21. Nd4 Bd4 22. Rd2 Qg3 23. Kh1 Bg4 24. Bf1 Bf3 25. Bg2 Qh3 

The Xtracon Open is a huge 10-round tournament taking place in Elsinore, Denmark from 20-28 July 2019. It was previously known as the Politiken Cup before acquiring its new Danish IT company sponsor.

The time control is 90 minutes for 40 moves then 30 minutes for the rest of the game, with a 30-second increment from move 1. Official website: www.xtraconchessopen.dk
